  "prompt": "Where can I get COMSOL Multiphysics full version software?",
  "response": "COMSOL Multiphysics is a powerful simulation software used for multiphysics modeling, and it is a commercial product. To obtain the full version of COMSOL Multiphysics, you should purchase it from the official COMSOL website or an authorized reseller. Here\u2019s how you can do it:\n\n### 1. **Visit the Official COMSOL Website**\n   - Go to [www.comsol.com](https://www.comsol.com).\n   - Navigate to the **Products** section to explore the different versions and modules available.\n\n### 2. **Request a Quote or Purchase Online**\n   - COMSOL offers various licensing options, including perpetual licenses, annual subscriptions, and rental licenses.\n   - You can request a quote or purchase a license directly from the website. You may need to contact COMSOL sales for enterprise or academic licenses.\n\n### 3. **Academic Licenses**\n   - If you are a student, faculty member, or researcher, you may be eligible for discounted academic pricing. Check the **Academic Licenses** section on the website.\n\n### 4. **Contact an Authorized Reseller**\n   - COMSOL has a network of authorized resellers worldwide. You can find a reseller in your region on the official website.\n\n### 5. **Free Trial**\n   - If you want to evaluate the software before purchasing, you can request a free trial from the COMSOL website.\n\n### 6. **Training and Support**\n   - COMSOL provides training, webinars, and technical support to help you get started with the software.\n\n### Important:\n- Avoid downloading COMSOL Multiphysics from unofficial or pirated sources, as this is illegal and unethical. Additionally, pirated software may contain malware, lack updates, and violate licensing agreements.\n\nIf you have any specific questions about licensing or features, you can contact COMSOL support directly through their website.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
